_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 9022, \"end\": 9028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Lorraine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.964195273042936e-18, \"text\": \"Lorena\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Lorraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Lorraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The goal quickly changed the momentum of the game, giving Team USA the upper hand.\", \"from\": 9078, \"to\": 9160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9136, \"end\": 9144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999627107, \"rank\": 3.7005907111963173e-11, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The score at halftime in the gold medal match between the USWNT and Brazil remained 0-0 after six minutes of stoppage time, but Brazil entered the locker room having put on a dominant performance.\", \"from\": 9164, \"to\": 9360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9222, \"end\": 9227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 9232, \"end\": 9238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999363354, \"rank\": 6.325578437708794e-11, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 9292, \"