Americans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The call was reviewed and no goal was rewarded.\", \"from\": 9972, \"to\": 10019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The USWNT is chasing a record fifth Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 10021, \"to\": 10076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10025, \"end\": 10030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nelly Korda was within striking distance of a gold medal at the2024 Paris Olympicsfor the first three days of competition, but she is sitting +3 on the day and 1-under par for the tournament after 17 holes on Saturday.\", \"from\": 10080, \"to\": 10298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10080, \"end\": 10091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelly_Korda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nelly Korda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelly_Korda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nelly_Korda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After putting a ball in the water at the 15th hole and triple bogeying the hole, Korda's medal hopes are on life support.\", \"from\": 10300, \"to\": 10421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The world no.1 ranked golfer struggled with the last four holes of the course all week.\", \"from\": 10423, \"to\": 10510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At one point during the second round, she held sole possession of second place before a quad bogey on the 16th\\u00a0hole followed by a bogey on the 17th\\u00a0hole.\", \"from\": 10511, \"to\": 10664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Barring something extraordinary, it seems unlikely Korda will medal in the women's Olympic Golf tournament.\